blog.name: sailor-rose-princess
blog.title: The Rosiest Rose
blog.description:
My main blog. Nonbinary - she/her and they/them pronouns - bisexual - birthday June 30th 1995 - adhd, depression, anxiety, BPD, synesthesia - Artist, sews outfits, Build a Bear enthusiast, and proud owner of the Lazytown Build a Bears. Often posts stuff from fandoms (mostly anime, Sailor Moon, Lazytown, Rocky Horror, Bob's Burgers, Homestuck, Disney, Hello Kitty, South Park, Captain Underpants, Samurai Jack, FLCL, Pee-wee Herman among others), recipes, cute stuff, fairy kei/lolita/j-fashion, mental health, body positivity, LGBT stuff (mostly try to stay on the positive side). Sometimes I take selfies and/or cosplays, or post art. I also like sewing Build a Bear outfits. My boyfriend is Nick aka des-rookie. Fair warning, I'm not a spoiler free blog, but I will tag stuff for spoilers.  Also if you want a certain trigger tagged, don't hesitate to ask me, I do my best to tag triggers, but if I miss something, let me know.  
Spoil me here:  http://www.amazon.com/registry/wishlist/2D7JUAKQ1ZPWH

summary: So would anyone be interested if I started selling handsewn Long Furbies?
body:
So would anyone be interested if I started selling handsewn Long Furbies?

I’m thinking of offering my services up to make and sell custom handsewn Long Furbies. These would be different from many of the other long Furbies you see, their faces are completely handsewn rather than using a Furby Buddy, but I can also use this as an advantage as I don’t have to rely on matching colors with a Furby buddy, and I won’t have to charge extra for a buddy I’d need to buy. I can make one in whatever colors you want (within reason, as I often get fabric from either WalMart or Jo-Ann’s, so I can’t be guaranteed with certain colors). I can also be creative with eye styles, and I can do different sizes and shapes (long and thin like a worm, shorter and thicker like a breadstick, you decide). I usually don’t use doll armatures with mine, but maybe I can add one for an extra charge. Maybe I’ll start a listing after the holidays. I’m thinking maybe 50 for about 3 feet, 75 for 6 feet, and add some extras for extra fees, like 15 bucks for an armature added, 10 bucks for a heartbeat effect added, and 5 bucks for a scent pad. You can choose colors (up to 3 colors), size/shape, and facial expressions at no extra charge (stripes may be a few bucks extra due to the extra work involved). Let me know what you guys think. It’s something I’d like to try out. Maybe I’ll start by selling a premade Long Furby or two to cut my teeth on.

summary: Dante’s ‘’ Inferno’’: The Second Circle: Minos:The Carnal Sinners. ‘’When Minos saw me, passing by the actions of his great...
caption:
Dante’s ‘’ Inferno’’: The Second Circle: Minos:The Carnal Sinners.

‘’When Minos saw me, passing by the actions of his great office, he said: ‘O you, who come to the house of pain, take care how you enter, and in whom you trust, do not let the width of the entrance deceive you.’ And my guide replied: ‘Why do you cry out? Do not obstruct his destined journey: so it is willed, where what is willed is done: demand no more.’ Now the mournful notes begin to reach me: now I come where much sorrowing hurts me.’’
